lead_paragraph: Republican presidential candidate Donald Trump's campaign on Tuesday inadvertently tweeted a promotional photo featuring what appeared to be Nazi German soldiers superimposed on the U.S. flag alongside the controversial real estate magnate's face.

headline.main: Trump Campaign Mistakenly Tweets Star-Spangled Nazis
